messages.text: Ah, I see I have your attention
Who is this? How do you know my name?
Is this some phone marketing thing?
Because I’m not interested, thank you
Oh you should be interested Martha
Please stop texting me or tell me if this is a joke
Goes by the name of Hailey
Has something happened to Hailey? She’s supposed to be in school
Yes, something has happened to her
Whoever you are, this is not funny.
I’m going to call you and let you speak to her
Do you see now, dear Martha? Did you hear her precious voice?
YOU BASTARD! WHAT HAVE YOU DONE TO HER
You’ve been a naughty girl Martha
Whoever you are please let her go
She’s just an innocent little kid
What then? Why are you doing this?
I’m going to give you some choices
If you play along, you’ll get to see Hailey again
Or at least what’s left of her
You SICK FREAK IF YOU TOUCH A HAIR ON HER BODY, IF YOU SO MUCH AS SCRATCH HER I’LL FIND YOU AND KILL YOU
But that’s a great idea for a test run
So your first test choice is:
Do you want me to shave all of Hailey’s hair off
Or would you like me to etch something nice into her skin?
That’s the choice. If you don’t choose, I’ll do both. You have 25 seconds
That was a very easy one. Hair is the obvious answer
Let’s chat while I do the cutting
Had to knock her out a bit haha
Tell me about your lover Martha
Please what can I do to make you stop
Would you like me to scratch his name in Hailey’s back?
OK OK I have oh God
Yes. Is that what you wanted? Yes I have been having an affair! Yes he’s 16! Yes it’s wrong! Now please give me my child back
But you need to be punished. So: which would you prefer having
A pinky finger, or five fingernails?
Ah yes, I told you the first one was a test run
By the way, she looks sort of cute with no hair
Your choice, Martha. Or both will happen...
You were a second too late
Buuut I’m feeling good today, so I’ll let this one slide
Fingernails grow back too, just very slowly
Let’s see, what else have you done
I’m divorced and I was lonely...
I never meant to hurt anyone
Well you DID MARTHA, YOU DID
My baby. Tell her I’m sorry. Please tell her
You also embezzled a LOT of money didn’t you
Want me to change my mind about the pinky finger?
OK OK I did, I DID! You beast! I don’t care! Just STOP hurting my daughter, PLEASE
Very good, Martha! You’re getting the hang of this
Still, you deserve to be punished
Hailey’s passed out. The fingernails were a bitch to pull out
Oh god oh god my baby
Buuut it’s time for the final choice
Or those lovely BLUE EYES of hers
PLEASE, take me instead! Do anything you like to me!
ANYTHING YOU WANT! Just leave her
WHAT ARE YOU DOING TO HER
Remember when you divorced me, took all my money and my daughter from me?
Well THAT’S how that felt, Martha
Nothing’s happened to her. It was a trick
But we will have a good long talk about custody and alimony now
THAT WAS YOU? YOU MONSTER! I’m going to call the police they’ll lock you up FOREVER. You’re SICK
If you do that, I’ll show them your little testimony about your affair with a minor and about embezzling funds.
That’s MUCH worse than a bit of harmless blackmail.
Who do you think will end up in jail and who will be free with Hailey?
Just wanted to make you see what it feels like to lose everything
So tomorrow I’ll come over for a chat. OK?
Wonderful! Hailey and I are getting ice cream now :)
